  "prompt": "Which is the best company to hire dedicated android app developers in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the best company to hire dedicated Android app developers in India depends on several factors such as project requirements, budget, timeline, and the specific expertise you're looking for. However, there are several well-regarded companies known for providing skilled Android developers:\n\n1. **Tata Consultancy Services (TCS)** - As one of the largest IT service companies in India, TCS offers a wide range of software development services, including mobile app development.\n\n2. **Infosys** - Known for its diverse talent pool and technological expertise, Infosys provides comprehensive app development services.\n\n3. **Wipro** - Wipro offers extensive application development and management services, including mobile app development, with a focus on technology innovation.\n\n4. **HCL Technologies** - Specializes in IT and software consulting with a strong reputation for mobile app development services.\n\n5. **Mindtree** - Offers dedicated mobile app development services, including Android app development, with a focus on agile methodologies.\n\n6. **Tech Mahindra** - Provides a wide range of IT services with skilled mobile app developers specializing in various technologies.\n\n7. **Hidden Brains** - Known for their innovation and skilled developers, they offer mobile app development services tailored to client needs.\n\n8. **Cognizant** - A major player in the IT services sector, offering robust app development solutions.\n\n9. **Appinventiv** - Specializes in mobile app development with dedicated teams for Android app development.\n\n10. **OpenXcell** - Known for its dedicated development teams and a strong presence in mobile app development.\n\nWhen selecting a company, consider their experience, portfolio of past projects, client testimonials, and technical expertise relevant to your project. It\u2019s also beneficial to discuss your project requirements and gauge how well the company understands and aligns with your business objectives.",
